  <h1>5 Best Newsletters That Exist & Effective Newsletter Examples</h1>

  <p><strong>We tend to subscribe to newsletters that interest us. The subject is one part of the newsletter. Then there are hundreds of newsletters on the subject we are interested in, so what do we do? How do we decide to subscribe to the best newsletter?</strong></p>
  <p>Newsletters have evolved over the years. From simple papers delivered to our homes, we now have colorful, modernly-designed digital newsletters sent to our emails. Still, we are in a pool of numerous newsletters.</p>
  <p>So how can we choose the best newsletter for us? Let’s answer this question by learning more about influential newsletters.</p>

  <h2>What are the types of newsletters?</h2>
  <p>There are various types of newsletters. Whatever you are interested in, you’ll find excellent newsletter content aiming to help you grow your interest and improve.</p>
  <p>Some of the most popular and effective ones are as the following:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Reporting</li>
    <li>Analysis</li>
    <li>Artistic</li>
    <li>Practical</li>
    <li>Curation</li>
    <li>Hybrid</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Moreover, any niche newsletter may include one of these types. The newsletters are such a great source of information that they offer solutions to every type of interest.</p>


  <h3>What are popular newsletter topics?</h3>
  <p>Each person’s interest varies. However, no matter what you are interested in reading, <strong>you can find the perfect newsletter</strong>.</p>
  <p>Some of the most popular newsletter topics are:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Business</li>
    <li>Technology</li>
    <li>Local or global news</li>
    <li>Fashion</li>
    <li>Lifestyle</li>
    <li>Environment</li>
    <li>Art</li>
  </ul>

  <p>Newsletters exist because they help people with relevant topics. We enjoy receiving newsletters. They are not dull advertising emails trying to sell something. Newsletters are tailored articles for subscribers only.</p>

  <h3>What makes newsletters effective?</h3>
  <p>We can call a newsletter effective when the audience reads it; they <strong>learn and relate to it a lot</strong>. They may even reference it if the newsletter can engage.</p>
  <p>Also, when the reader is looking forward to receiving the following newsletter, that indicates that the job is correct and it is a practical, informative, or entertaining newsletter.</p>
  <p>When the newsletter content is not interesting for the reader, they would not even finish reading the whole piece. So, of course, we prefer to choose newsletters that contribute to us and that appeal to us.</p>


  <h3>What are the five elements of an effective newsletter?</h3>
  <p><strong>Here we present the five elements of an effective newsletter.</strong> Pay attention to these features while deciding which newsletter to subscribe to.</p>

  <ol>
    <li>Have intent</li>
    <p><strong>An effective newsletter must have clear goals for each publication.</strong> So when you open it and read it, you’ll know the newsletter's intent.</p>

    <li>Visual with attractive design</li>
    <p><strong>We tend to read texts that appeal to our eye as well as the importance of the meaning</strong>. But, on the other hand, nobody likes a boring piece of paper or document with only letters. So you may also subscribe to a newsletter if you enjoy its visuals.</p>

    <li>Readable on mobile devices as well</li>
    <p><strong>While subscribing to a newsletter, we should consider its compatibility.</strong> We are in front of our laptops only sometimes, so a mobile device-friendly newsletter is an excellent choice to consume your favorite newsletters.</p>

    <li>Telling us a story</li>
    <p><strong>A newsletter prepared in a story format may entertain you if you read and listen to stories.</strong> Moreover, some newsletters craft narratives to be resumed in each publication, so waiting to see what happens next is exciting.</p>

    <li>Clear and informative content</li>
    <p><strong>While deciding which newsletter to subscribe to, pay attention to how the content is.</strong> If you need help understanding it initially, it may give an idea of how the following newsletters will be.</p>
  </ol>

  <h3>Best newsletter examples</h3>
  <p>We have compiled <strong>five outstanding newsletter examples</strong> for you. Depending on your area of interest, you may find some amusing.</p>

  <ol>
    <li><%= link_to 'Recomendo', 'https://www.getrevue.co/profile/Recomendo/', target: '_blank' %></li>
    <p>Recomendo is an entertaining weekly newsletter with over <strong>fifty thousand subscribers</strong> and has <strong>334 issues published</strong>.</p>
    <p><strong>It gives six simple but very efficient recommendations every week.</strong> Additionally, each recommendation is by six different people who are experts in their area.</p>
    <p>It’s a practical, entertaining, and teaching newsletter for anyone.</p>

    <li><%= link_to 'Watching', 'https://www.nytimes.com/newsletters/watching', target: '_blank' %></li>
    <p>Watching is <strong>a newsletter by New York Magazine</strong>. They publish weekly, and in each edition, <strong>they recommend the latest movies and TV shows</strong>.</p>
    <p>They classify movies separately for each platform, such as Netflix, Hulu, and Amazon Prime, and make specific recommendations weekly. As a result, they help you save time choosing what to watch.</p>
    <p>Watching is excellent for people who love quality content on digital streaming platforms.</p>

    <li><%= link_to 'The Moz Top 10', 'https://moz.com/moztop10', target: '_blank' %></li>
    <p>Moz is a competitive SEO tool, and The Moz Top 10 is its newsletter published once every two weeks. The newsletters include <strong>the top 10 valuable articles about digital marketing and SEO.</strong></p>
    <p>Moz uses its company features to find the highest-ranking articles and shares them with its subscribers. As subscribers to this newsletter, we can examine the most successful themes and see what makes them successful.</p>
    <p>This newsletter is great for digital marketers, SEO experts, and content writers.</p>

    <li><%= link_to 'Creative Mornings Weekly Highlights', 'https://us2.campaign-archive.com/home/?u=b8d0c821758ac4979998d6301&id=1768cc808f', target: '_blank' %></li>
    <p>Creative Mornings, a creative community, is the architect behind this excellent newsletter series. <strong>The weekly newsletters highlight interesting lectures around the world.</strong></p>
    <p>The subjects range from technology to design. They also recommend some links to quality content.</p>
    <p>This newsletter is perfect for creative people or people who are interested in learning about design and decoration.</p>

    <li><%= link_to 'CNN’s 5 Things', 'https://edition.cnn.com/specials/5-things', target: '_blank' %></li>
    <p>CNN’s 5 Things is a newsletter sent to your email informing you about the top 5 must-know morning news.</p>
    <p>Once subscribed, CNN lets you know the most important daily news. The news could be politics, world news, or new technological inventions. CNN decides that and sends it to you.</p>
    <p>This newsletter is fabulous for those who are busy yet want to make sure to get all important news.</p>
  </ol>

